description: AG joins Shannon again to chat about their last-minute plans for Coachella and the absurd outfits they have planned. They tell you the *actual* key to having sex with either of them and Shannon gives a final update on WiFi guy. What’s a chucklefucker? Is Anna Grace a serial killer? TBD. We read your confessions and tell some of our own in episode 4. Go Cubs!
